OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely dry
OL,6,Fthis evening with bright spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping. Remaining dry overnight
OL,8,Fwith clear periods, although some
OL,9,Fisolated fog patches may develop as
OL,10,Fthe wind eases.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FDry with cloudy periods and
OL,13,Fperhaps some fog patches to start,
OL,14,Fsunny spells developing by the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Becoming warm or very warm
OL,16,Fin places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
