OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FVery
OL,6,Fwarm for most during this period, hot
OL,7,Fin places, with sunny spells. Mostly
OL,8,Fdry, with perhaps one or two showers
OL,9,Fin the far east on Saturday.
